data.description: Come, see this rare find in Pleasant Hill! 4BR 3BA W/O ranch with gorgeous hardwood floors in upper family room, new in 2017. New carpet in LL and BR’s, and new paint throughout most of the home. Light fixtures and fan in kitchen, dining area and family room new in 2023. Quick close available, this one won’t last! Seller is offering $5000 towards closing costs with an acceptable offer.
